<p>If you were in the room during the talk, Iâ€™m sure the experience is still viscerally available to you, but for those who were not, I think Karlâ€™s post falls far short of the necessary description to underscore the problem. As I said in a <a href="https://twitter.com/AmeliaMN/status/942962475418505216">recent tweet</a>, itâ€™s hard to convey in words how icky the talk was. But, Iâ€™m going to make an attempt.</p>

